PrecisAcceptance of AMENDMENTS to a DESIGNATION made by the KAMLOOPS BAND in 1996 which correct errors in the legal description of two parcels of land within Kamloops Indian Reserve No. 1 in British Columbia, removes a parcel included by error and revokes the designation insofar as it relates to another section of that Reserve.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of AMENDMENTS to a DESIGNATION made by the KAMLOOPS BAND in 1996
which correct errors in the legal description of two parcels of land within
Kamloops Indian Reserve No. 1 in British Columbia, removes a parcel
included by error and revokes the designation insofar as it relates to
another section of that Reserve.
